{"questionId":"d5718376-6a71-41d6-aa0f-411bb7f3bb75_10","correctAnswer":"7","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Substitute into the function","content":"With $g(x)=\\tfrac{6x-1}{5}$, replace $x$ with $6$: $$g(6)=\\tfrac{6(6)-1}{5}=\\tfrac{35}{5}.$$"},{"title":"Simplify","content":"$$g(6)=7.$$ The answer is <strong>7</strong>."}]}